Package: steeper
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3, gir1.2-unity-5.0, gir1.2-gtk-3.0, gir1.2-notify-0.7, gir1.2-gdkpixbuf-2.0, pulseaudio-utils, sound-theme-freedesktop
Description: Simple tea steeping timer (mainly for Unity)
 A simple egg-timer type application to help you manage your tea steeping time.
 Rings an alarm and displays an desktop notification, when the tea is ready.
 Supports saving several pre-set timers as well as brew duration increments.
